    {
      "id": "task_1756808438217_5mh2xejxu",
      "title": "Setup comprehensive test coverage reporting and CI/CD integration",
      "description": "Implement comprehensive test coverage reporting system and integrate with CI/CD pipeline to enforce coverage requirements and ensure production-ready quality.\n\nCOVERAGE REPORTING REQUIREMENTS:\n- Configure vitest coverage reporting with detailed metrics\n- Set up coverage thresholds (100% for critical modules, 90% for others)\n- Generate HTML coverage reports for detailed analysis\n- Implement coverage badges and metrics dashboard\n- Create automated coverage trend tracking\n\nCI/CD INTEGRATION:\n- Enforce coverage requirements in CI pipeline\n- Block deployment if coverage falls below thresholds\n- Automated test execution on all PRs\n- Coverage diff reporting for code changes\n- Integration with GitHub Actions or similar CI/CD\n\nMONITORING AND ALERTS:\n- Coverage regression detection\n- Automated alerts for coverage drops\n- Performance monitoring for test execution\n- Test failure notifications and reporting\n- Quality gate enforcement\n\nSUCCESS CRITERIA:\n- Automated coverage reporting working\n- CI/CD pipeline enforcing coverage requirements\n- Clear visibility into coverage metrics\n- Quality gates preventing regression\n- Production-ready monitoring and alerting",
      "mode": "DEVELOPMENT",
      "category": "test-setup",
      "priority": "high",
      "status": "pending",
      "dependencies": [],
      "important_files": [
        ".github/workflows/",
